      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Skill: SkillContractAuthoring\n\n**Category:** Validation / Contract Authoring\n\n**Intent:** Validate Skill / Contract graphs against the v1 contract, report missing interface or safety surfaces, and only propose bounded metadata repairs.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
        "_classBinding": {
