    {
      "id": "skill-contract-skill-scope",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Scope",
      "position": {
        "x": -980,
        "y": 380
      },
      "width": 720,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Scope\n\nThis skill:\n- validates v1 node membership\n- validates that a contract has identity, scope, interface, law, safety, failure, and procedure surfaces\n- reports missing or ambiguous contract structure\n- keeps overlapping field names aligned when meaning matches\n\nThis skill does NOT:\n- invent a new skill purpose\n- rewrite normative law without review\n- replace domain-specific contract meaning",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
